WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 16]

01:48.000 --> 01:48.620
It's you?

01:50.710 --> 01:51.620
It's me.

01:53.920 --> 01:54.820
We meet again,

01:57.640 --> 01:58.930
old friend.

02:21.910 --> 02:23.460
You once told me

02:24.520 --> 02:26.770
that besides the Spirit-Binding Ring on your hand,

02:28.800 --> 02:30.210
the other half of the Spirit-Storing Jade

02:31.310 --> 02:33.180
had been sealed inside the Mist-Blood Cave,

02:34.120 --> 02:37.020
the most treacherous, perilous place in the world.

02:38.150 --> 02:39.340
One wrong step,

02:40.430 --> 02:42.020
and you'd die without a trace.

02:43.190 --> 02:43.970
But look.

02:45.310 --> 02:47.460
I still went there, took the jade,

02:48.030 --> 02:49.650
and turned it into a magical artifact.

02:56.080 --> 02:57.090
Pretty, isn't it?

02:58.750 --> 03:00.140
You're going to such lengths

03:00.680 --> 03:02.210
to obtain the Dragon Deity's Power.

03:04.280 --> 03:05.370
What exactly is that for?

03:07.000 --> 03:09.140
I don't believe you're only acting on Jiu Ying's orders.

03:11.030 --> 03:12.060
What for?

03:16.520 --> 03:17.770
Naturally,

03:23.120 --> 03:25.930
to drag you down from that hollow divine throne.

03:38.430 --> 03:38.900
Ji Ling!

03:42.470 --> 03:43.370
Stay.

03:59.840 --> 04:01.770
Don't force me to use Word Magic on you again.

04:04.120 --> 04:06.060
My power may be weaker than yours,

04:07.680 --> 04:08.800
but I'm on guard against you

04:08.800 --> 04:10.340
every second now.

04:11.120 --> 04:12.140
It won't be that easy

04:13.190 --> 04:14.060
for you to control me.

04:23.820 --> 04:25.740
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

04:28.220 --> 04:30.140
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

04:38.780 --> 04:41.220
♪Don't be sad♪

04:41.260 --> 04:42.980
♪Through every yesterday♪

04:43.140 --> 04:45.660
♪Don't you cry♪

04:45.660 --> 04:47.380
♪Through every memory♪

04:47.500 --> 04:53.180
♪I'll always stay with you♪

04:53.580 --> 04:55.420
♪Stay with you♪

05:01.310 --> 05:02.010
Shiguang.

05:07.600 --> 05:08.420
Shiguang.

05:09.310 --> 05:10.130
Shiguang.

06:07.340 --> 06:13.020
♪Dream's faint glow slowly turns to frost♪

06:13.500 --> 06:19.500
♪The setting sun leaves behind a trace of iris scent♪

06:19.510 --> 06:20.660
Wu Shiguang?

06:21.260 --> 06:27.100
♪Lend me one more fleeting dream I never want to wake from♪

06:27.380 --> 06:33.700
♪So I can gather a handful of langxi grass and let it steep in my heart♪

06:37.310 --> 06:38.100
Wu Shiguang.

06:38.100 --> 06:40.700
♪An island in the sky...♪

06:41.240 --> 06:42.220
Wu Shiguang.

06:44.390 --> 06:45.450
Wu Shiguang.

06:51.000 --> 06:51.620
It's all right.

06:52.190 --> 06:52.930
I'm right here.

06:55.100 --> 07:01.340
♪Yet time does not fade or grow old...♪

07:01.600 --> 07:02.220
I...

07:02.920 --> 07:03.860
I...

07:04.800 --> 07:05.740
You don't have to say anything.

07:09.120 --> 07:09.980
I understand.

07:12.000 --> 07:12.490
I...

07:16.390 --> 07:17.180
I'm just...

07:18.600 --> 07:20.540
a little tired.

07:21.750 --> 07:23.220
I want you to stay...

07:24.800 --> 07:25.570
with me.

07:31.750 --> 07:32.300
Why

07:33.360 --> 07:34.780
didn't you leave earlier?

07:35.870 --> 07:37.370
I'm blind.

07:38.720 --> 07:40.370
Where could I have gone?

07:44.780 --> 07:50.420
♪The one in my dream sits lightly by the water...♪

07:53.310 --> 07:54.570
It's so cold here.

07:57.720 --> 07:59.140
I want to go home.

07:59.140 --> 08:04.340
♪Lend me a beam of moonlight to light the long way I've come...♪

08:04.560 --> 08:05.100
I'm afraid

08:06.800 --> 08:07.540
we won't

08:08.560 --> 08:10.130
get the Star Stone after all.

08:15.490 --> 08:16.460
It's all right.

08:18.680 --> 08:20.100
At least Wu Shiguang

08:21.560 --> 08:22.930
has left

08:26.070 --> 08:27.180
safely.

08:31.560 --> 08:32.260
Do you remember?

08:34.130 --> 08:36.700
You still owe me a favor.

08:39.150 --> 08:39.900
How about this?

08:40.510 --> 08:41.810
Grant me one request after we get out.

08:42.720 --> 08:43.300
All right.

08:46.020 --> 08:52.100
♪Crash into a heart wall, bitter and soft...♪

08:52.120 --> 08:52.690
Go ahead.

08:53.480 --> 08:54.330
Whatever it is,

08:55.160 --> 08:56.210
I promise I'll do it.

08:58.060 --> 08:58.900
I'll do it.

09:01.670 --> 09:02.210
Don't...

09:03.600 --> 09:07.020
don't hate me.

09:42.750 --> 09:43.660
Why isn't it working yet?

09:58.750 --> 09:59.260
It worked!

10:00.510 --> 10:01.380
Lucky us.

10:01.790 --> 10:02.540
Now we can save them.

10:03.320 --> 10:03.690
Let's go.

10:11.640 --> 10:13.540
What happened?

10:14.200 --> 10:15.250
Is this discrimination against demons?

10:31.480 --> 10:32.420
With lustrous light,

10:32.960 --> 10:33.900
let all evil be undone!

11:13.720 --> 11:14.610
Good thing I got sent here.

11:15.270 --> 11:16.850
Had it been the skinny Hua Qi instead,

11:17.240 --> 11:18.420
he wouldn't have been able to carry you.

11:21.550 --> 11:22.180
Open up!

11:23.030 --> 11:23.570
Open up!

11:24.390 --> 11:24.850
Open up!

11:25.240 --> 11:26.260
I'm still out here!

11:26.480 --> 11:26.900
Open up!

11:35.240 --> 11:36.450
Master... Master Xi?

11:54.440 --> 11:54.850
Father?

11:55.910 --> 11:56.610
Chi, get back.

11:57.670 --> 11:58.730
That isn't Xie Lingxi.

11:59.750 --> 12:00.500
That's Jiu Ying.

12:03.270 --> 12:04.100
How did Jiu Ying

12:04.100 --> 12:05.020
turn into Master Xi?

12:06.720 --> 12:07.850
Before Xie Lingxi died,

12:08.360 --> 12:09.570
he left behind the last of his power

12:10.030 --> 12:11.330
in his own tombstone

12:11.790 --> 12:13.060
to protect Wu Shiguang.

12:13.960 --> 12:16.210
But unexpectedly, his great power

12:17.000 --> 12:19.090
also drew in Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

12:19.790 --> 12:21.900
Who would've thought? After 1,000 years,

12:22.870 --> 12:24.630
I still got the chance

12:24.630 --> 12:26.020
to take root in the Star Stone.

12:28.080 --> 12:29.300
All these years,

12:30.000 --> 12:31.660
those double-flower hunters

12:31.670 --> 12:33.380
have destroyed so many of my spirit fragments.

12:33.790 --> 12:35.020
Despicable.

12:35.360 --> 12:36.330
And now they've

12:36.360 --> 12:37.970
delivered themselves right to my door.

12:39.510 --> 12:41.330
I'll let them all die in there.

13:07.360 --> 13:07.970
Father.

13:12.670 --> 13:13.140
Father,

13:14.150 --> 13:14.730
what do we do?

13:16.750 --> 13:17.690
I can't beat him.

13:19.120 --> 13:20.180
Don't give up.

13:20.960 --> 13:22.810
Stop making a fool of yourselves here.

13:23.630 --> 13:25.540
The Star Stone is about to shatter.

13:26.440 --> 13:27.260
They'll be

13:28.150 --> 13:29.660
trapped inside forever.

13:30.910 --> 13:32.020
Even a tiny ant

13:32.910 --> 13:35.060
can bring down a mighty dragon or elephant.

13:35.790 --> 13:37.020
Even a mayfly

13:37.670 --> 13:39.730
can shake a towering tree.

13:42.120 --> 13:42.730
Chi,

13:43.840 --> 13:45.380
do you remember our family motto?

13:47.440 --> 13:48.260
"Do your best."

13:50.910 --> 13:51.780
I know

13:53.480 --> 13:55.140
that even though you say it

13:55.480 --> 13:56.420
all the time,

13:57.270 --> 13:58.970
you've never truly lived by it.

14:00.750 --> 14:01.690
But today,

14:03.270 --> 14:04.660
I will teach you what it really means

14:05.360 --> 14:07.420
to do your best.

14:08.360 --> 14:09.490
This fire striker

14:09.600 --> 14:11.540
is the sacred artifact of the weasel clan.

14:12.030 --> 14:13.570
Its name is Ember.

14:15.360 --> 14:16.370
If it senses

14:16.370 --> 14:18.140
that you truly mean to give everything you've got,

14:19.000 --> 14:20.060
it will unleash a power

14:20.360 --> 14:21.850
that can burn through anything.

14:33.150 --> 14:35.060
Weasels should crawl back

14:35.060 --> 14:36.090
into their holes.

15:27.390 --> 15:30.450
No!

15:32.870 --> 15:33.330
Father!

15:35.510 --> 15:36.260
Wonderful, Father!

15:37.320 --> 15:38.140
You were amazing.

15:38.360 --> 15:39.180
You beat Jiu Ying.

15:39.440 --> 15:41.090
Our clan is finally going to be famous.

15:41.510 --> 15:42.420
We've produced a great hero.

15:44.000 --> 15:44.930
This is such an honor.

15:47.320 --> 15:47.930
What's wrong?

15:49.320 --> 15:50.450
You silly child,

15:51.360 --> 15:52.810
after today, no one will beat you

15:54.600 --> 15:55.380
ever again.

15:57.480 --> 15:58.500
Have you forgotten the family motto?

15:58.550 --> 15:58.970
No, I haven't.

15:59.790 --> 16:00.850
Didn't you fail to do your best?

16:01.120 --> 16:01.380
I...

16:01.480 --> 16:02.380
I really did try my best.

16:02.380 --> 16:02.730
You...!

16:03.900 --> 16:05.940
♪Burns out quick, no reason why...♪

16:05.960 --> 16:06.380
Father.

16:06.480 --> 16:07.180
Father, what's wrong?

16:12.120 --> 16:13.090
Good boy,

16:15.960 --> 16:17.180
I hope you'll

16:19.000 --> 16:21.020
keep your feet on the ground,

16:22.270 --> 16:24.330
take everything seriously,

16:25.600 --> 16:27.360
and always do your best.

16:27.360 --> 16:27.780
Father...

16:28.080 --> 16:28.730
Father, get up.

16:29.150 --> 16:30.330
I'll take you to Wu Shiguang.

16:30.480 --> 16:31.570
He has the Dragon Deity's Power.

16:31.790 --> 16:32.880
He can save you,

16:32.880 --> 16:33.300
Father!

16:34.720 --> 16:35.380
Father!

16:39.000 --> 16:39.420
Father!

16:40.840 --> 16:41.420
Father...

16:45.340 --> 16:46.660
♪Every line cuts deep♪

16:46.660 --> 16:48.300
♪Head held high, I charge ahead...♪

16:48.670 --> 16:49.420
Father!

16:50.390 --> 16:50.850
Father...

16:52.220 --> 16:53.860
♪No matter how heavily fate weighs me down♪

16:53.980 --> 16:59.340
♪The sky is still behind me♪

17:00.060 --> 17:01.300
♪Don't fear the pain...♪

17:02.320 --> 17:02.770
Father...

17:03.180 --> 17:06.660
♪Father said life is never easy♪

17:07.050 --> 17:08.700
♪Keep pressing on♪

17:08.980 --> 17:12.580
♪Do your very best and be a hero...♪

17:17.480 --> 17:18.260
Father...

17:20.440 --> 17:21.370
I promise...

17:22.550 --> 17:24.170
I promise I'll do my best.

17:24.590 --> 17:25.170
Father...

17:26.720 --> 17:28.060
I'll never be like that again.

17:29.090 --> 17:29.640
Father...

17:30.010 --> 17:30.940
Remember...

17:30.940 --> 17:32.280
I promise...

17:32.280 --> 17:33.460
No matter what you are...

17:33.460 --> 17:34.810
Father, I promise...

17:34.830 --> 17:36.300
- Or how capable you are... - Father...

17:37.310 --> 17:39.060
Always give it everything you've got

17:39.400 --> 17:40.570
and do your best.

17:41.880 --> 17:44.100
Only then can you live with no regrets.

17:44.100 --> 17:49.180
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

18:42.510 --> 18:43.130
You Chi.

18:49.830 --> 18:50.300
I...

18:51.440 --> 18:52.460
I don't have a father anymore.

19:03.240 --> 19:04.570
We're out of the illusion now.

19:05.240 --> 19:06.020
Why is he still unconscious?

19:06.960 --> 19:07.980
Take him back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:08.880 --> 19:09.540
I'll examine him there.

19:15.000 --> 19:16.570
I already put the fragment in my pouch.

19:17.510 --> 19:18.540
Why can my artifact

19:19.000 --> 19:20.330
still sense Jiu Ying's evil aura?

19:21.440 --> 19:22.700
Let's take them back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:23.240 --> 19:24.780
Once we turn in these two spirit fragments of Jiu Ying's,

19:25.680 --> 19:26.650
there will only be

19:27.390 --> 19:28.770
three left in the world.

19:29.400 --> 19:30.640
But those last three

19:30.640 --> 19:31.890
still haven't been detected at all.

19:32.720 --> 19:33.410
What a headache.

19:40.000 --> 19:41.610
We're taking Commander Li back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:42.510 --> 19:43.090
You Chi,

19:44.200 --> 19:46.540
your father was a hero.

19:47.310 --> 19:49.020
He saved all our lives.

19:51.640 --> 19:52.370
Take care.

20:11.000 --> 20:11.700
Shiguang.

20:15.620 --> 20:16.330
You again?

20:29.200 --> 20:29.850
Master.

20:32.160 --> 20:33.020
You've grown up.

20:40.110 --> 20:41.370
This is only a trace of power

20:42.030 --> 20:43.370
I left behind to protect you.

20:45.070 --> 20:46.500
I can't hold this human form for long.

20:47.510 --> 20:48.260
Protect me?

20:55.160 --> 20:56.810
So you've been protecting me all along.

20:58.590 --> 20:59.410
No wonder Wu Shiguang

20:59.440 --> 21:00.570
always manages to escape danger.

21:01.400 --> 21:03.020
It was thanks to your protection

21:04.640 --> 21:05.460
that I wasn't killed

21:06.270 --> 21:08.300
by the curse on that beast trap.

21:09.880 --> 21:10.370
Am I right?

21:13.240 --> 21:15.170
No wonder it only worked with Wu Shiguang's blood.

21:16.920 --> 21:18.370
As you probably know now,

21:19.750 --> 21:21.330
my hands were once stained with blood.

21:23.590 --> 21:25.020
Among the blood of sinners,

21:25.720 --> 21:26.740
mine is there too.

21:29.510 --> 21:30.570
I, too, was one of the guilty.

21:39.750 --> 21:40.590
All the memories I had

21:40.590 --> 21:42.090
when I was alive are stored inside.

21:42.830 --> 21:43.540
My blood

21:44.030 --> 21:45.540
resonates with my true form

21:46.310 --> 21:48.540
and awakens the memories buried within.

21:49.790 --> 21:50.460
And that

21:51.720 --> 21:53.220
accidentally dragged all of you

21:53.350 --> 21:54.300
into my memories.

21:55.750 --> 21:56.330
Master,

21:56.960 --> 21:58.130
in the Star Stone illusion,

21:59.000 --> 21:59.540
you said

22:00.550 --> 22:01.610
you promised Chi Wen

22:02.030 --> 22:03.170
you'd protect someone for him.

22:06.790 --> 22:07.460
Who was it?

22:11.590 --> 22:12.810
You already know the answer,

22:14.960 --> 22:15.540
don't you?

22:21.270 --> 22:22.300
He asked you to look after me

22:23.200 --> 22:23.980
and guide me.

22:25.480 --> 22:27.130
Was it because he felt guilty after slaughtering

22:28.070 --> 22:28.980
the flood dragon clan?

22:32.830 --> 22:33.890
Didn't you see the truth

22:35.750 --> 22:37.300
in the illusion?

22:38.590 --> 22:39.700
Chi Wen wasn't the one

22:40.960 --> 22:42.060
who slaughtered the flood dragons.

22:44.590 --> 22:45.850
The culprit

22:47.440 --> 22:49.060
was always searching for a dragon's descendant.

22:54.240 --> 22:54.650
I...

22:58.440 --> 22:59.940
Am I Chi Wen's child?

23:00.550 --> 23:01.370
Of course not.

23:03.830 --> 23:04.810
You are his younger brother.

23:06.830 --> 23:07.410
You are

23:08.880 --> 23:09.850
the Tenth Dragon Son.

23:16.550 --> 23:17.170
Shiguang,

23:18.480 --> 23:20.300
you remember the dragon-scale birthmark

23:21.000 --> 23:22.260
on your chest, right?

23:25.440 --> 23:27.130
Before the Nine Dragons sacrificed themselves

23:28.350 --> 23:29.700
and transformed into a vast mountain range

23:30.240 --> 23:31.460
to seal Jiu Ying away,

23:32.200 --> 23:34.700
each of them removed their most precious reverse scale.

23:35.400 --> 23:36.570
Those scales fused together

23:37.200 --> 23:38.170
and became the Dragon Stone.

23:39.680 --> 23:41.370
I stood watch as that Dragon Stone gave birth.

23:43.720 --> 23:44.780
And so you came into being.

23:45.830 --> 23:47.020
You are the world's

23:49.110 --> 23:50.090
tenth dragon.

23:54.000 --> 23:54.780
I'm a dragon?

23:56.790 --> 23:58.020
Ever since the flood dragons were wiped out,

23:58.720 --> 23:59.740
for all these decades,

24:00.830 --> 24:02.200
I've spent every day and night

24:02.200 --> 24:03.370
training in the spells you taught me.

24:06.460 --> 24:08.460
♪Oh, the scars of this life♪

24:08.660 --> 24:09.500
♪I embrace the moonlight♪

24:09.500 --> 24:12.420
♪I embrace the shackles♪

24:12.620 --> 24:16.260
♪Who do those undying golden scales shine for?♪

24:16.740 --> 24:20.060
♪Who has the frozen sea buried away?♪

24:20.340 --> 24:21.380
♪A sliver of inner darkness♪

24:21.460 --> 24:26.220
♪Love and hate tear at me as the snow cuts deep♪

24:26.620 --> 24:32.260
♪I fold the past and rewrite the threads of the story♪

24:32.860 --> 24:38.860
♪You're waiting for me up ahead♪

24:39.550 --> 24:40.330
My hatred for dragons

24:40.350 --> 24:41.330
was what kept me going,

24:42.750 --> 24:44.610
dragging out this painful life.

24:47.880 --> 24:48.610
And now, after all this time,

24:51.590 --> 24:52.940
you're telling me

24:53.640 --> 24:54.410
I'm a dragon?

24:56.350 --> 24:57.260
I'm a dragon?

25:03.160 --> 25:04.740
So the flood dragons weren't wiped out because of Chi Wen.

25:10.680 --> 25:11.650
It was because of me!

25:27.550 --> 25:28.740
Even I didn't realize

25:29.960 --> 25:31.370
those Shilin Sect hunters

25:32.400 --> 25:33.980
were actually Jiu Ying in disguise.

25:35.960 --> 25:36.850
I thought the Dragon Deity...

25:41.440 --> 25:42.020
Chi Wen?

25:45.720 --> 25:46.330
What about him?

25:48.640 --> 25:49.220
Nothing.

25:50.880 --> 25:51.410
Master,

25:54.920 --> 25:56.540
why didn't you tell me sooner?

25:58.590 --> 25:59.220
Shiguang,

26:01.480 --> 26:02.960
your birth was tied to a heavy duty

26:02.960 --> 26:03.980
from the start.

26:05.640 --> 26:06.700
I wanted you

26:06.700 --> 26:07.980
to have

26:09.750 --> 26:10.940
a carefree childhood

26:11.350 --> 26:13.020
before you learned the truth.

26:14.160 --> 26:14.980
I never expected

26:15.680 --> 26:17.700
your identity would bring disaster to the flood dragons.

26:21.200 --> 26:22.410
The Dragon Deity's Power

26:23.030 --> 26:24.000
has already begun

26:24.000 --> 26:24.980
entering your body, hasn't it?

26:28.480 --> 26:29.370
His body?

26:30.880 --> 26:31.980
Isn't the Dragon Deity's Power

26:32.270 --> 26:34.260
stored in the prayer beads?

26:34.510 --> 26:35.260
Of course not.

26:38.160 --> 26:38.940
First the scales.

26:39.790 --> 26:40.650
Then the claws.

26:41.400 --> 26:42.330
Then the horns.

26:43.480 --> 26:44.410
And finally, the eyes.

26:45.550 --> 26:46.740
Each time one share of the Dragon Deity's Power

26:46.750 --> 26:47.740
enters your body,

26:48.240 --> 26:49.060
a petal-shaped scale mark

26:49.640 --> 26:51.780
will appear on your forehead.

26:53.680 --> 26:54.500
It is the sign

26:55.680 --> 26:57.540
that you're gradually becoming a dragon.

26:58.680 --> 27:00.540
Once you gather all four shares of the Dragon Deity's Power,

27:01.070 --> 27:02.460
you'll become a true dragon.

27:03.200 --> 27:03.810
Then,

27:05.200 --> 27:07.020
you'll naturally understand everything.

27:07.960 --> 27:09.000
For now, let me

27:09.000 --> 27:10.220
give you a hand

27:11.270 --> 27:13.370
in obtaining the second share of the Dragon Deity's Power.

27:54.590 --> 27:56.020
Will he end up like Xiaowei?

27:57.550 --> 27:59.300
Once the Dragon Deity's Power leaves the body,

28:00.310 --> 28:01.740
there's no turning back.

28:36.440 --> 28:37.090
Old friend,

28:38.480 --> 28:39.090
I'm here.

28:44.440 --> 28:45.260
I did it.

28:47.440 --> 28:48.610
The Star Stone is whole again,

28:49.550 --> 28:50.170
and it's shining again.

28:51.000 --> 28:52.260
Can you free my clansmen

28:53.240 --> 28:54.610
from petrification now?

28:59.400 --> 29:00.300
I can't.

29:03.440 --> 29:04.540
Do you still hate me?

29:17.680 --> 29:18.780
You were born the Star Stone

29:18.890 --> 29:20.130
with the whole world in your heart.

29:22.070 --> 29:23.540
But because of me,

29:24.110 --> 29:26.460
the world came to see you as evil.

29:26.680 --> 29:27.780
You should hate me.

29:28.240 --> 29:29.090
I'm a sinner.

29:35.000 --> 29:35.650
But please,

29:37.200 --> 29:38.570
save my clansmen.

29:39.030 --> 29:40.090
They're innocent.

29:40.590 --> 29:41.740
They're in too much pain.

29:58.640 --> 29:59.740
I've never hated you.

30:02.680 --> 30:03.780
I just can't do it.

30:05.510 --> 30:08.540
The petrification spell cannot be reversed.

30:09.350 --> 30:10.300
Since ancient times,

30:11.680 --> 30:13.020
that has always been the case.

30:15.200 --> 30:15.890
That's impossible.

30:18.440 --> 30:19.300
That's impossible.

30:20.240 --> 30:21.650
Master Chi Wen told me

30:22.310 --> 30:23.650
to find the Star Stone.

30:23.680 --> 30:25.540
As long as the Star Stone still exists in this world,

30:25.640 --> 30:26.850
there is still hope.

30:27.110 --> 30:28.170
Find the Star Stone,

30:28.510 --> 30:29.740
undo the petrification,

30:29.830 --> 30:31.810
and make amends for your sins.

30:32.240 --> 30:32.940
He said

30:34.110 --> 30:35.890
the Star Stone could save my clansmen.

30:36.750 --> 30:38.540
I asked Chi Wen to say that.

30:40.890 --> 30:41.650
Back then,

30:43.000 --> 30:44.460
you imprisoned yourself in the Blackwater River.

30:45.830 --> 30:46.850
Your will had collapsed.

30:47.590 --> 30:48.890
All you wanted was to die.

30:50.030 --> 30:51.220
So I thought

30:52.160 --> 30:53.570
that maybe if you had hope,

30:54.880 --> 30:56.170
you'd keep living.

31:00.880 --> 31:01.810
I understand now.

31:02.880 --> 31:04.570
You kept lying to Wu Zhiqi,

31:05.750 --> 31:06.740
saying you hated him,

31:07.790 --> 31:08.650
but really,

31:09.720 --> 31:11.140
you were afraid that once he learned

31:11.140 --> 31:12.570
that petrification couldn't be undone,

31:12.960 --> 31:14.780
he would lose the will to live.

31:15.720 --> 31:17.130
You chose to die

31:18.070 --> 31:19.170
so Wu Zhiqi could keep living.

31:24.110 --> 31:24.700
Master...

31:25.750 --> 31:27.980
Hope is like a tree that grows in the Ruined Sand.

31:30.400 --> 31:31.940
Take the Crying Elm for example.

31:32.920 --> 31:34.880
Though it takes root

31:34.880 --> 31:36.220
deep in scarred and battered soil,

31:37.590 --> 31:40.220
its branches still climb toward the light.

31:44.220 --> 31:50.260
♪I am a little fish, yet you never cast your net♪

31:51.300 --> 31:57.300
♪I am a wild horse, yet you dare let me run free...♪

32:01.070 --> 32:02.020
Only with hope

32:03.270 --> 32:05.330
can dead wood put out branches again.

32:07.830 --> 32:09.170
Hope is also like a seed.

32:10.240 --> 32:11.850
It needs time to grow

32:12.960 --> 32:14.300
and time to heal.

32:17.030 --> 32:18.740
When winter passes,

32:20.160 --> 32:21.300
reunion will come.

32:21.640 --> 32:22.410
Xizai?

32:28.200 --> 32:29.540
But what you gave me

32:33.240 --> 32:34.260
wasn't a seed.

32:35.640 --> 32:37.610
It was a lifeless stone.

32:38.550 --> 32:40.740
That's why I've come to tell you the truth.

32:41.920 --> 32:43.540
The grudges of these past centuries

32:44.960 --> 32:46.260
should come to an end now.

32:51.590 --> 32:52.300
Bai Ze,

32:53.790 --> 32:55.370
I have one final wish.

32:57.030 --> 32:58.650
Please ask Master Dragon Deity

33:01.550 --> 33:03.500
to destroy my petrified clansmen.

33:04.830 --> 33:05.740
Destroy them.

33:09.070 --> 33:09.850
Put them

33:11.920 --> 33:13.370
out of their misery.

33:14.940 --> 33:15.500
♪So please♪

33:15.740 --> 33:21.180
♪I save my deepest love for you alone...♪

33:21.200 --> 33:21.850
Old friend.

33:24.110 --> 33:24.740
Old friend...

33:30.020 --> 33:35.940
♪You are a rising tide, bringing a melody of highs and lows♪

33:37.020 --> 33:43.220
♪All my troubles are forgotten here♪

33:43.740 --> 33:50.060
♪Only you and I remain in our tiny world...♪

33:53.750 --> 33:54.850
You old geezer.

33:56.680 --> 33:58.300
When we were drinking earlier,

34:00.400 --> 34:01.330
for one moment,

34:02.680 --> 34:03.960
I really felt like you were a friend

34:03.960 --> 34:05.260
I could tell anything to.

34:05.260 --> 34:11.300
♪I truly cherish the sweetness in your smile♪

34:12.320 --> 34:12.980
Master...

34:47.610 --> 34:53.540
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow♪

34:54.700 --> 34:59.980
♪Let them chase the skies, I'll stay with you below...♪

35:00.000 --> 35:00.650
Shiguang,

35:01.800 --> 35:03.090
you are the only one in this world

35:03.550 --> 35:04.610
I still can't let go of.

35:05.480 --> 35:06.420
Though I am gone,

35:07.400 --> 35:08.540
the Star Stone remains.

35:09.280 --> 35:10.500
If you find yourself in dire straits one day,

35:11.480 --> 35:12.690
it may yet help you once.

35:14.550 --> 35:15.460
But remember this.

35:16.000 --> 35:17.380
The Star Stone's power is too great.

35:18.030 --> 35:19.060
Do not use it rashly.

35:20.760 --> 35:21.420
Master...

35:21.980 --> 35:22.620
♪So please♪

35:22.820 --> 35:32.660
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:34.840 --> 35:35.610
Stop.

35:51.070 --> 35:51.770
Yuan Wuhuo,

35:52.590 --> 35:53.290
your name

35:54.070 --> 35:55.250
was meant to be a blessing.

35:56.070 --> 35:56.860
But now,

35:57.230 --> 35:59.090
you have become Jiu Ying's pawn,

35:59.920 --> 36:01.460
bringing disaster upon the world.

36:03.320 --> 36:05.570
Xiaowei and Wu Zhiqi,

36:06.190 --> 36:07.940
driven by your manipulation,

36:08.280 --> 36:10.610
both walked down a path of self-destruction.

36:11.360 --> 36:12.290
Master Dragon Deity,

36:13.480 --> 36:14.460
you've got it wrong.

36:15.880 --> 36:17.820
My name is now Yuan Wuhuo.

36:18.840 --> 36:20.460
"Wuhuo" as in "to gain nothing."

36:21.360 --> 36:22.690
I've long come to a realization.

36:23.550 --> 36:25.170
Life is fleeting

36:25.590 --> 36:27.060
and filled with every kind of suffering.

36:28.150 --> 36:29.730
Whatever one spends a lifetime chasing,

36:30.480 --> 36:32.130
in the end, it all amounts to nothing.

36:32.710 --> 36:35.340
Only by no longer clinging to gain and possession

36:35.360 --> 36:36.820
can one stop fearing loss.

36:38.070 --> 36:39.820
Only with neither loss nor gain

36:40.760 --> 36:43.420
can one remain true to one's real self.

36:46.280 --> 36:47.170
I never thought

36:49.320 --> 36:50.250
you would come back.

36:51.880 --> 36:52.860
You should never have returned.

37:57.840 --> 37:58.500
What is it?

37:59.920 --> 38:02.340
Are you starting to feel the strain?

38:03.670 --> 38:05.690
You don't have much demon power left, do you?

38:15.320 --> 38:16.940
The water of the Blackwater River

38:17.480 --> 38:19.290
can absorb demon power.

38:20.110 --> 38:21.540
Wu Zhiqi imprisoned himself here

38:21.540 --> 38:22.820
back then

38:24.440 --> 38:25.900
because he wanted to die.

38:27.030 --> 38:27.860
So

38:30.230 --> 38:32.020
that's why you lured me here on purpose.

38:32.960 --> 38:34.540
So many years have passed,

38:36.800 --> 38:39.250
but you're as unguarded as ever.

39:18.480 --> 39:19.610
Wrathful sandstorm,

39:20.190 --> 39:21.290
grant me your power.

40:07.960 --> 40:08.770
Dragon Deity's Power?

40:53.060 --> 40:54.220
♪It's your light♪

40:54.420 --> 40:56.300
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

40:56.460 --> 40:59.580
♪That set the night alight♪

40:59.940 --> 41:06.460
♪And lead me through the fight♪

41:08.220 --> 41:10.100
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

41:10.540 --> 41:14.980
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

41:15.780 --> 41:17.460
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

41:17.620 --> 41:23.020
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

41:23.780 --> 41:29.180
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

41:31.500 --> 41:37.540
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

41:38.500 --> 41:40.660
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

41:40.940 --> 41:45.780
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

41:46.140 --> 41:48.460
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

41:48.660 --> 41:53.740
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

41:53.980 --> 41:55.980
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

41:56.260 --> 42:00.620
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

42:01.620 --> 42:08.580
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

42:25.140 --> 42:28.100
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

42:29.180 --> 42:32.580
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

42:33.380 --> 42:35.900
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

42:36.140 --> 42:39.220
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

42:39.620 --> 42:41.940
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

42:42.460 --> 42:46.860
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

42:47.100 --> 42:49.260
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

42:49.660 --> 42:54.620
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

42:54.860 --> 42:56.020
♪It's your light♪

42:56.220 --> 42:58.060
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

42:58.260 --> 43:01.380
♪That set the night alight♪

43:02.140 --> 43:11.580
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
